205	/**
206	 * Rehydrate a draft for the resume/edit flow. Owner-checked; only drafts
207	 * (not published/scanning/etc.) are returned. The form values come from
208	 * the same shape ManifestFormSchema produces so the wizard can drop them
209	 * in without remapping.
